ActRoyal Canadian Mounted Police Act
PrecisDesignation of DOUGLAS E. MOEN, Q.C., of Regina, Saskatchewan, a part-time member of the Management Advisory Board for the Royal Canadian Mounted Police, as Chairperson of the Management Advisory Board for the Royal Canadian Mounted Police, to hold office during pleasure for a term of nine months or until such time as a new Chairperson is designated, whichever occurs first.
